OL,3,CMan sentenced to two years for series
OL,4,Cof assaults on emergency staff
OL,6,FA Jersey man who has been sentenced to
OL,7,Ftwo years in prison for a series of
OL,8,Fassaults, citing his primary reason
OL,9,Ffor his actions was: "I'm a little bit
OL,10,Fof a d***".
OL,12,FGlen Rhys Le Claire, 32, appeared in
OL,13,FJersey's Royal Court on Friday 3
OL,14,FJanuary 2025.
OL,16,FHe pleaded guilty to one charge of
OL,17,Flarceny and five counts of assault
OL,18,Fcommitted over a period between mid-
OL,19,FMay and early August this year.
