OL,3,CMan sentenced to two years for series
OL,4,Cof assaults on emergency staff
OL,6,FAll six charges took place when Le
OL,7,FClaire was intoxicated.
OL,9,FSome later offences were committed
OL,10,Fwhile Le Claire was already under
OL,11,Finvestigation and on bail for earlier
OL,12,Fcrimes.
OL,14,FOne of the assaults was against a
OL,15,Fparamedic, and another was against a
OL,16,Fpolice officer carrying out their duty.
