OL,3,CMan sentenced to two years for series
OL,4,Cof assaults on emergency staff
OL,6,FLieutenant Bailiff Anthony Olsen MBE -
OL,7,Fthe Jurat who read the sentence - told
OL,8,Fthe court that it was "clear" that the
OL,9,Fparamedic was "trying to help" and was
OL,10,F"caring and gentle" in their approach.
OL,12,FHe added that a custodial sentence was
OL,13,Fneeded as Le Claire was a "high risk
OL,14,Fof reconviction".
OL,16,FLe Claire had 13 previous convictions
OL,17,Finvolving a total of 36 offences,
OL,18,Fincluding two assaults on the police
OL,19,Fand an assault on his mother.
