OL,3,CMan sentenced to two years for series
OL,4,Cof assaults on emergency staff
OL,6,FBefore sentencing, Le Claire told the
OL,7,Fcourt: "My mother dearest does
OL,8,Feverything for me, so I believe I
OL,9,Fshould serve the longest sentence due
OL,10,Fto that breach of trust."
OL,12,FHe also apologised repeatedly but
OL,13,Fadmitted an apology doesn't do much to
OL,14,Fhelp his victims.
OL,16,FLe Claire explained: "It wasn't (...)
OL,17,Fso much alcohol as who I am (...) I'm
OL,18,Fa little bit of a d***."
